messages.message:
based on the comment at the top of this Dockerfile (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/blob/master/shared-utils/py-utils/data-api-utils/Dockerfile), it seems it's used to build docs for Refiner?

we can wait for Lydia to come back from OOO tomorrow to confirm, but since we're no longer changing the enterprise platform, we probably don't need to generate new docs for Refiner anymore?
